"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-2024-0727-1462135-korea-olympics-gaffe\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee has apologised for a gaffe during the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics in which South Korean athletes were incorrectly introduced as North Korean.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.8717497073714261, \"rank\": 0.14711824036978816, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}, {\"begin\": 181, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.8717497073714261, \"rank\": 0.14711824036978816, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the South Korean delegation sailed down the Seine River in the French capital, they were introduced with the official name for North Korea: \\\"Republique populaire democratique de Coree\\\" in French, then \\\"Democratic People's Republic of Korea\\\" in English.\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.8717497073714261, \"rank\": 0.14711824036978816, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}, {\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998860034995514, \"rank\": 0.00010181632808845543, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.407553184070528e-14, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998860034995514, \"rank\": 0.00010181632808845543, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We deeply apologise for the mistake that occurred when introducing the South Korean team during the broadcast of the opening ceremony,\\\" the IOC said in a post on its official Korean-language X account.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.8717497073714261, \"rank\": 0.14711824036978816, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}, {\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.953171015907171e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The error sparked displeased reactions in South Korea, a global cultural and technological powerhouse that is technically still at war with the nuclear-armed and impoverished North.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4286813720980762e-14, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea's sports ministry said in a statement it \\\"expresses regret\\\" over the \\\"announcement during the opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics, where the South Korean delegation was introduced as the North Korean team\\\".\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4286813720980762e-14, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.8717497073714261, \"rank\": 0.14711824036978816, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.8717497073714261, \"rank\": 0.14711824036978816, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Second vice sports minister Jang Mi-ran, a 2008 Olympic weightlifting champion, has asked for a meeting with IOC chief Thomas Bach to discuss the matter, it added.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jang_Mi-ran\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jang Mi-ran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jang_Mi-ran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jang_Mi-ran\"}, {\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.953171015907171e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sports ministry has also asked the foreign ministry to \\\"deliver a strong protest to the French side\\\" over the issue, the statement said.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998860034995514, \"rank\": 0.00010181632808845543, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea's National Olympic Committee plans to meet with the Paris Olympics Organising Committee and the IOC to voice their protest, request measures to prevent a recurrence, and send an official letter of protest under the name of the head of its delegation, the sports ministry said.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4286813720980762e-14, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999673293967177, \"rank\": 3.256099702251958e-05, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.953171015907171e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"North Korea was correctly introduced with the country's official name.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.407553184070528e-14, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Relations between the two Koreas are at one of their lowest points in years, with the North bolstering military ties with Russia while sending thousands of trash-carrying balloons to the South.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1853, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999990517060218, \"rank\": 4.919709996518483e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response, Seoul's military blasts K-pop and anti-regime messages from border loudspeakers and recently resumed live-fire drills on border islands and near the demilitarised zone that divides the Korean peninsula.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.9999999930669219, \"rank\": 3.787315030275513e-09, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\"}, {\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Korean peninsula\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:AFP    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2194, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 2219, \"end\": 2226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999999991044433, \"rank\": 8.9